Package: rcheckers
Title: Russian Checkers Game
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Vladimir", "Ivanov", email = "Vlladdimmir@yandex.ru", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An implementation of Russian Checkers (Shashki) using the R Shiny framework.
    Features include a fully interactive game board, strict rule enforcement (including mandatory captures),
    support for both PvP (Player vs Player) and PvE (Player vs AI) modes, and a bilingual interface (English/Russian).
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
